=left class=m><span class=title> UBERGUILDS - Question for you.</span><hr size=1> How many TAGGED people does it take you to kill:<br><br>#1. AoW<br><br>#2. Burrower Parasite<br><br>#3. Tunare<br><br>#4. Creator<br><br><br>The &quot;uberguild&quot; on Torvonnilous usually has between 60-70 TAGGED people including 10 level 60 NTOV equipped Warriors, 8-10 level 60 Rogues, and 8-10 60 clerics.<br><br>Is 60-70 people on a raid considered &quot;Zerging&quot;?<br><br>Thanks for HONEST answers. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uvalicsoulpierce.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ValicSoulpierce</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_thatch.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/19/02 4:11:26 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: UBERGUILDS - Question for you.</span><hr size=1> you shouldn't *need* more than 40 people to do anything in the game.  Try thinking of strat's more than numbers. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ufiramas.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Firamas</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/19/02 4:13:25 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: UBERGUILDS - Question for you.</span><hr size=1> We generally have 60+ people there for AoW raids.. partially because people get psyched into thinking that much is necessary, partly because everyone wants loot from it.  =)  It'd be doable with 40-45 fairly easily assuming we kept the number of clerics the same.<br><br>Parasite 45-55 usually show up, once again doable with less though.  The hard part isnt the last fight, its not being stupid with aggro/mana management for the first rounds.<br><br>Tunare isn't that hard anymore.<br><br>And Creator is a friggin joke. =) <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ufiramas.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Firamas</A> at: 3/19/02 4:14:33 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=lancetorv>LanceTorv</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/19/02 4:16:55 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: UBERGUILDS - Question for you.</span><hr size=1> Consider Swiller a troll..<br><br>He's looking for bait to harass Blades of Wrath on Torv, that's all this is.<br><br>His guild (Sacrosanct) was recently disbanded due to poor management, and he's been on a insult spree vs. every other guild on the server for the past 2 weeks.<br><br>You can find his words of wisdom here :<br><br><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub46.ezboard.com/fdivinity14264frm5.showMessage?topicID=396.topic">pub46.ezboard.com/fdivini...=396.topic</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br><br>Also, read his remaining posts on <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.torvonnilous.net/,">www.torvonnilous.net/,</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> our server's main messageboard, where he was finally banned for insulting everyone and their mother.<br><br>He's a bitter, bitter person.<br><br>And on topic, &quot;Swiller,&quot; it really doesn't matter how many people a guild has to kill things.  You'll find most uber guilds have 50 plus people.<br><br>Do all of them ever raid at once? No.<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=lancetorv>LanceTorv</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/19/02 4:18:02 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: UBERGUILDS - Question for you.</span><hr size=1> Oops, that was supposed to be<br><br><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.torvonnilous.net/">www.torvonnilous.net/</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br><br>Accidentally added a comma at the end. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukarthunk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Karthunk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/19/02 4:39:35 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: UBERGUILDS - Question for you.</span><hr size=1> Yeah, we call the first 40 people to show for raids actual guild members and the other 18 to show afterwards zerglings. <br><br>Karthunk..... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usashanna.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sashanna</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/19/02 5:14:22 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: UBERGUILDS - Question for you.</span><hr size=1> go away troll <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ugrimmlokk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Grimmlokk</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://grimmlokk.homestead.com/files/icon.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font 